CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper December 29, 1951, pg. 13, reads: "Budding Artist - A Promising Art Student and Her Work... Bottom right: 'These here professors are getting me down!'... - Harris Photos."
TitMainTitle: Peggy Owens (Skillen) wearing light colored smock and seated on stool with hands on head, surrounded by paintings in art studio, Carnegie Tech (Carnegie Mellon University)
